title: Sections 445-171 and 445-172 not to apply
context: §437-42 Sections 445-171 and 445-172 not to apply. Sections 445-171 and 445-172 do not apply to dealers and salespersons licensed under this chapter. [L 1939, c 258, §25; RL 1945, §7385; am L 1951, c 90, pt of §1; RL 1955, §160-186; am L 1957, c 302, §1(27); am L 1961, c 59, §1(16); HRS §437-42; gen ch 1993]
